      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "The Spirit of the Lord revealed"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "His will to saints of old;"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "Their heart and mind lips unsealed"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "His glory to unfold."
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "Amid the gloom of ancient night"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "They hailed the dawning Word,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "And in the coming of the light"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "Proclaimed the coming Lord."
        }
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "The prophets passed; at length there came"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "To sojourn and abide,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "The Word incarnate, to whose name"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "The prophets testified;"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "And He, the twilight overpast,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Himself, the Light of light,"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "As man with man, revealed at last"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "The Father to our sight."
        }
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "number": 1,
          "text": "Eternal Spirit, who dost speak"
        },
        {
          "number": 2,
          "text": "To mind and conscience still,"
        },
        {
          "number": 3,
          "text": "That we in this our day, may seek"
        },
        {
          "number": 4,
          "text": "To do our Fatherâ€™s will,"
        },
        {
          "number": 5,
          "text": "To us the word of life impart,"
        },
        {
          "number": 6,
          "text": "Of Christ, the living way;"
        },
        {
          "number": 7,
          "text": "Give us the quiet, humble heart"
        },
        {
          "number": 8,
          "text": "To hear and to obey."
        }
      ],
      "number": 3
    }
  ],
  "title": "The Spirit of the Lord Revealed"
